name: #00035 Portrait of Mummy 210125
description: #00035 Portrait of Mummy 210125 Created January 25th 2022 Is a crayon drawing of mummy, this drawing is a big step forward from previous attempts at drawing form and features, Iris was very proud she captured her mummy's eyes, mouth and hair and a neck connecting to the head. This is NFT number 35 released by the Youngest Artist in the NFT World, Iris. Age at release - 3 years old.
